### Create customer (required fields only)
POST http://localhost:3003/api/customer
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": " Maria Silva ",
  "email": "maria.silva@example.com"
}

### Create customer (with optional phone and nif)
POST http://localhost:3003/api/customer
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Jean Dupont",
  "email": "jean.dupont@example.com",
  "phone": "+33 6 12 34 56 78",
  "nif": 123456789
}

### Create customer — missing email (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:3003/api/customer
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Missing Email"
}

### Create customer — unauthenticated (expect 401/403)
POST http://localhost:3003/api/customer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "No Auth",
  "email": "no.auth@example.com"
}
